{"tid":1080026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國防部撥78億興建圍牆","createTime":"2019-03-27T10:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T12:06:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"593a4a1f59ca6fd0e0c32698a367b3565f926440","tid":1080026,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190327/20642280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F20642280&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=52d0b6f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F20642280&h=a60da1c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190327/20642280</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國防部撥78億興建圍牆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190327/large/a1706a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190327%2Flarge%2Fa1706a.gif&h=4c48c39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部撥款10億美元（78億港元）興建美墨圍牆，撥款將用作興建5.5米高、92公里長的「行人路圍欄」、進行道路工程和安裝照明系統。<br />\n<br />\n國防部前日發聲明指，署理國防部長沙納漢（Patrick Shanahan，圖）已批准陸軍工兵部隊司令開始計劃和使用10億美元支援國土安全部、海關和邊境保衞局；聲明又引述聯邦法例指，國防部有權建設道路、圍欄和安裝照明設備，以堵截邊境販毒路線，和支持有關當局的掃毒行動。<br />\n<br />\n月前被國會拒絕撥款57億美元（444.6億港元）建牆的特朗普上月15日頒佈緊急狀態令，圖繞過國會取得撥款，被參眾兩院通過議案推翻，他月初再否決兩院議案。兩院須分別集得2/3大比數票才能推翻他的否決，料難以成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風季將缺人力重建災區<br />\n<br />\n沙納漢昨日到國會為國防部草擬的預算案辯護，為因此而受影響的150個項目、逾43億美元（335.4億港元）解釋。該些項目中至少有一半涉及美軍駐海外的軍事基地。軍方內部表示擔憂，指還有數月將再迎來風季，不夠人力於北卡州和喬治亞州的災區重建。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司/法新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n嘲受傷示威長者 馬克龍捱轟"},{"pid":"9ba31976577cda85503a6f59196a6f485cccd4b1","tid":1080026,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"Great wallllllllll?"},{"pid":"974687b2a10bb1caf6aecdc2f8a70f9117e98996","tid":1080026,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"is good <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmxC340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmxC340.jpg&h=3f7e82f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}